                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                            },
                            "page": 238
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "text": "Countless adventures begin in a tavern or a pub. Maybe it's because such places attract the risk-prone, or maybe it's because everyone needs a little liquid courage before they decide to take on a group of rampaging ogres.",
